{"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setTargetCoordinate:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"CLLocationCoordinate2D","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@CLLocationCoordinate2D"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"targetCoordinate","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"animated:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"BOOL","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"animated","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"completionHandler:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"text":" (^)()) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"completion","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"targetCoordinate","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The target coordinate to fit within the viewport.","type":"text"}]}]},{"name":"animated","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If ","type":"text"},{"code":"YES","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", the map animates to fit the target within the map","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"view. If ","type":"text"},{"code":"NO","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", the map fits the target instantaneously.","type":"text"}]}]},{"name":"completion","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The block executed after the animation finishes.","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"By default, the target coordinate is set to an invalid coordinate, indicating"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"that there is no target. In course tracking mode, the target forms one of two"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"foci in the viewport, the other being the user location annotation. Typically,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the target is set to a destination or waypoint in a real-time navigation scene."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"As the user annotation moves toward the target, the map automatically zooms in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to fit both foci optimally within the viewport."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This method has no effect if the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"userTrackingMode"},{"type":"text","text":" property is set to a value"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"other than "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserTrackingMode\/MLNUserTrackingModeFollowWithCourse"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]}]}],"abstract":[{"text":"Sets the geographic coordinate that is the subject of observation as the user","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"location is being tracked, with an optional transition animation and completion","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"handler.","type":"text"}],"sections":[],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/setTargetCoordinate:animated:completionHandler:"},"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setTargetCoordinate:animated:completionHandler:","kind":"identifier"}],"remoteSource":{"fileName":"MLNMapView.h","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.h#L799"},"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setTargetCoordinate:animated:completionHandler: